{"tid":2415212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳撤港台隔離令 免羅致光入營","createTime":"2021-02-20T05:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T05:52:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"351d8b74c038f48fed27bcbcd791221a6bda8481","tid":2415212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/POASLRD52RCPZEGDIVZGWFQ5EU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FPOASLRD52RCPZEGDIVZGWFQ5EU%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbktOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=cec5c6a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FPOASLRD52RCPZEGDIVZGWFQ5EU%2F&h=4dbe51bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/POASLRD52RCPZEGDIVZGWFQ5EU/</a><br />\n<br />\n傳撤港台隔離令 免羅致光入營<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8bFKYjS2OB6ejaCieqzR8skE4IU=/2692x1795/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KMNAZ7RTBRFU7BUOGHQJDIVXPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8bFKYjS2OB6ejaCieqzR8skE4IU%3D%2F2692x1795%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKMNAZ7RTBRFU7BUOGHQJDIVXPM.jpg&h=6dfdf6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■歐家榮<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港電台繼一名髮型師確診後，再多一名助理編導初步確診。有消息指，衞生防護中心曾計劃擴大檢疫範圍，將所有到過港台化妝間的人送入檢疫中心，當中包括曾於《議事論事》中受訪的勞福局局長羅致光，但其後計劃又撤銷，令人質疑是因為羅致光而「彈弓手」，衞生防護中心聲稱檢疫不會考慮任何人的背景。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：孕婦 重病者 不宜接種科興  專家：長者數據太少 想知答案強人所難<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衞署：。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，港台曾收到衞生防護中心要求，將所有2月9至11日到過化妝間的人士，不論是否接觸髮型師，均全部送往檢疫中心，但其後又撤銷計劃。記者昨日問衞生防護中心是否因為羅致光而「彈弓手」？歐家榮稱，中心界定密切接觸者是基於科學及風險評估，「唔會考慮任何人嘅背景」。"},{"pid":"de516fa172dde59919e2fafc9c5541dcf7cffc13","tid":2415212,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"即係會考慮<br />\n上次老舞群組d有錢佬有冇入營<br />\n係香港,香港人連二等公民都冇資格做"}]}